title: Roebuck Inn
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Beer/Wine, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A general pub offering everyday food. With a change of owners came vegan choices. The wine, including sparkling and champagne, are vegan. On Sunday a vegan nut roast on a Sunday. During the week 2 or so main vegan dishes. The roast potatoes are cooked in oil and the gravy is vegan. Has vegan sausage. Kitchen keeps soya milk, vegan ice cream, vegan cream and custard for substitution. Sticky toffee pudding, chocolate brownie, and bread and butter pudding are all vegan.
